QuestData.Title: Worn Obleron Etching
QuestData.Description:
<The etching on the crumbling manuscript hints at the origins of the Maw.
Ve'nari would be fascinated by this.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring the Worn Obleron Etching to Ve'nari at Ve'nari's Refuge.
QuestData.RewardText:
<Ve'nari glances over the manuscript.>
This is truly an ancient document. A pity it is in such poor condition. The secrets it holds must be priceless.
